        ": سَأَلْتُهُ عَنِ اَلرَّضَاعِ فَقَالَ \"لاَ يَحْرُمُ مِنَ اَلرَّضَاعِ إِلاَّ مَا اِرْتَضَعَ مِنْ ثَدْيٍ وَاحِدٍ حَوْلَيْنِ كَامِلَيْنِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4674 - Ubayd ibn Zurarah narrated from Zurarah from Abu Abdullah (as) who said: I asked him about breastfeeding, and Imam (as) said:\n\"Breastfeeding does not create a prohibition except when a child nurses from one breast for two complete years.\""
        ]
      }
